                        <strong>Where to paste</strong>
                        <p>Add this code directly into your website's HTML body, a markdown file, or a blog post editor (using the HTML/Source view).</p>
                        
                        <strong>Customizing the code</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li><code>width</code> & <code>height</code>: Controls player size. Accepts numbers for pixels (e.g., <code>560</code>) or percentages (e.g., <code>100%</code>).</li>
                            <li><code>border-radius</code>: Modify the <code>style="border-radius: 16px;"</code> snippet to change how rounded the corners are.</li>
